the company of the children of Israel, saying, The land, which we passed through to search it, is an exceeding good land.","year":-1490},{"id":"recE7kj6dDjDYh2eW","ref":"Num.14.8","text":"If the LORD delight in us, then he will bring us into this land, and give it us; a land which floweth with milk and honey.","year":-1490}]}
